<div id="pf3946" class="pf w51 h237" data-page-no="3946"><div class="pc pc3946 w51 h237"><div class="t m715 xd3 h35 y2a60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">courts of heaven there awaits them an </div><div class="t m618 xd3 h35 y2ac8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;eternal weight of glory.&quot; </div><div class="t m1b1 x3 h35 y28b1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Wherefore seeing we also are com-</div><div class="t ma4f xd3 h35 y2ac7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">passed about with so great a cloud of </div><div class="t m7d8 xd3 h35 y28f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">witnesses, let us lay aside every weight, </div><div class="t m894 xd3 h35 y1c1e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the sin which doth so easily beset </div><div class="t m114b xd3 h35 y239d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us, and let us run with patience the </div><div class="t m5be xd3 h35 y2314 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">race that is set before us, looking unto </div><div class="t m8c2 xd3 h35 y20f0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus the author and finisher of our </div><div class="t m576 xd3 h35 y717 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">faith.&quot; &quot;Our light affliction, which is but </div><div class="t mb8b xd3 h35 y396 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for a moment, worketh for us a far more </div><div class="t m2da xd3 h35 y8ad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">exceeding and eternal weight of glory; </div><div class="t mb47 xd3 h35 ya66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">while we look not at the things which </div><div class="t mbe0 xd3 h35 y373 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are seen, but at the things which are </div><div class="t ma3e xd3 h35 y466 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not seen; for the things which are seen </div><div class="t m51 xd3 h35 yf69 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are temporal; but the things which are </div><div class="t m78b xd3 h35 y1c9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not seen are eternal.&quot; </div><div class="t m580 x1c h35 y2b41 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When the redeemed stand in the pres-</div><div class="t m59f x1f h35 y2a18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ence of God, they will see how short-</div><div class="t m118e x1f h35 y2a58 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sighted were their conclusions as to </div><div class="t m368 x1f h35 y2ac9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what Heaven records as success. They </div><div class="t m7d4 x1f h35 y29e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will see how petty were their supposed </div><div class="t m2a2 x1f h35 y23a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trials, and how unreasonable were their </div><div class="t m787 x1f h35 y2348 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doubts. They will see how often they </div><div class="t m900 x1f h35 y2315 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">brought failure to their work by failing </div><div class="t m172b x1f h35 y44f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to show unquestioning faith in God. </div><div class="t m6d4 x1f h35 y509 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">From the lips of the angelic choir and </div><div class="t m2b9 x1f h35 y398 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the redeemed host will peal forth the </div><div class="t ma4a x1f h35 y846 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">chorus: &quot;Great and marvelous are thy </div><div class="t maaa x1f h35 y555 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works, Lord God Almighty; just and true </div><div class="t md06 x1f h35 y1bbd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are thy ways, thou King of saints. Who </div><div class="t m87b x1f h35 y7ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shall not fear thee, 0 Lord, and glorify </div><div class="t m492 x1f h35 y50e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thy name? for thou only art holy.&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m3b0 x1f h35 y65d ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m992 x67 h35 y1227 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 7, 1912. </div><div class="t m758 x175 h5 y22c8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">103 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
